white throughout the frontend ‚Äî page shell, cards/panels, section/card headers, tab strips,
toolbars, hover surfaces, the breadcrumb, and the OntoViz canvas. Borders, status/semantic
tints (success/danger/info), scrollbar thumbs, interaction overlays (`rgba(0,0,0,.1/.15)`)
