   `#e9ecef` / `#f0f0f0`, translucent `rgba(248,249,250,‚Ä¶)`, and grey-only `linear-gradient`s)
   to white across ~30 area CSS files and the inline `style="‚Ä¶background‚Ä¶"` strings in a few
   JS/HTML templates. Only `background` / `background-color` declarations were touched ‚Äî
   borders, `fill`, chart data colours, and `!important` disabled cues were preserved.

