## UI: business-user home page reshape (KPI band + All Domains gateway)

**Context**: The home page was builder/jargon-first (hero tagline "...RDF, OWL, and
R2RML standards", a Save/Load/Reset domain panel, a 3-step build workflow, and three
OWL/R2RML/Digital-Twin info cards). Requested a reshape "really for a business user".
Confirmed direction: the home is the **open door for all domains** and **KPIs are the
priority content** (not a per-user role-gated view ‚Äî roles belong to domains). Pure
front-end change reusing existing cheap endpoints (`/domain/info`, `/session-status`,
`/list-projects`); no backend changes.

**Changes**:
1. `src/front/templates/home.html` ‚Äî restructured into five sections:
   (1) value-first hero ("Explore and govern your organization's knowledge‚Ä¶");
   (2) **Current Domain KPI / health band** ‚Äî a 6-tile `.ob-kpi-tile` row (Entities,
   Relationships, Mappings, Quality, Status, Version) replacing the old 3 `.stat-item`
   tiles; (3) **All Domains** gateway grid (`#domainGateway` / `.ob-domain-grid`) ‚Äî the
   open door to every domain; (4) My Tasks (unchanged); (5) a demoted **Build & Manage**
   section that folds the Step 1/2/3 workflow cards and the New/Manage/Data Sources/
   Save/Load buttons. Dropped the jargon-heavy OWL/R2RML/Digital-Twin info cards. Wired
   the new `home/css/home.css` in `extra_css`.
2. `src/front/static/home/css/home.css` (new) ‚Äî `.home-kpi-band` grid, `.ob-domain-grid`
   / `.ob-domain-card` gateway styles (with `.is-current` highlight + empty-state CTA),
   and the `.home-build-header` row. All colours via `--db-*` tokens; KPI tiles reuse the
   shared `.ob-kpi-tile` component.
3. `src/front/static/home/js/home.js` ‚Äî rewrote: `loadHomeStatus()` fetches `/domain/info`
   (status, version, precision score, stats) + `/session-status` in parallel and renders
   the six KPI tiles (Quality tile colours by precision threshold: ‚â•80 success / ‚â•50
   warning / else danger; Status tile renders a DRAFT/IN-REVIEW/PUBLISHED badge);
   `loadDomainGateway()` fetches `/list-projects`, renders one card per domain (current
   domain highlighted) and opens a domain via `POST /domain/load-from-uc` (latest/active
   version) then routes to `/domain/`; the `data-action` handler is now delegated from
   `document` so New/Save/Load/Reset keep working from the demoted section.
4. `src/front/static/global/css/pages.css` ‚Äî removed the now-unused `.session-stats` /
   `.stat-item*` and `.info-cards` / `.info-card*` rules (and the `.domain-panel
   .session-stats` spacing rule) superseded by the KPI band.
5. `tests/units/api/test_ui_rendering.py` ‚Äî replaced `test_stat_items` (asserted the old
   `classCount` / `propCount` / `mappingCount` ids) with `test_kpi_band` (the six new
   `kpi*` ids) and added `test_domain_gateway` (`#domainGateway`).

